trans-unit.source: Converts a value that represents the location (target) in which to display the content resulting from a Web navigation to a string.
trans-unit.target: 將表示因 Web 巡覽而顯示內容之位置 (目標) 的值轉換成字串。

trans-unit.source: This class also converts a string to a target value.
trans-unit.target: 這個類別 (Class) 也將字串轉換成目標值。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TargetConverter> class creates a collection of values that can be used to specify the location in which to display content resulting from a Web navigation, such as the page navigated to when a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink> control is clicked.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TargetConverter>類別會建立可以用來指定要在其中顯示內容所產生的 Web 功能，例如網頁瀏覽至時的位置的值集合<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink>按一下控制項時。

trans-unit.source: This collection is commonly used in a designer to display a list of values that can be used for the `Target` property of a navigation control, such as the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink> control.
trans-unit.target: 這個集合通常在設計工具用來顯示數值的清單，可用於`Target`巡覽的屬性控制，例如<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink>控制項。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TargetConverter" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TargetConverter" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext" /> that provides a format context.
Returns a collection of standard values from the default context for the data type this type converter is designed for.
trans-unit.target: 從為這個型別轉換子所設計的資料型別預設內容中，會傳回標準值的集合。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter.StandardValuesCollection" /> containing a standard set of valid values, or <see langword="null" /> if the data type does not support a standard set of values.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter.StandardValuesCollection" /> 含有標準有效值的集合，如果資料型別不支援標準值集合，則為 <see langword="null" />。
這是僅供內部使用的類別。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext" /> that provides a format context.

Returns a value that indicates whether the collection of standard values returned from the <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TargetConverter.GetStandardValues(System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext)" /> method is an exclusive list.
trans-unit.target: 傳回值，表示從 <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TargetConverter.GetStandardValues(System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext)" /> 方法傳回的標準值集合是否為獨佔清單。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter.StandardValuesCollection" /> returned from <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TargetConverter.GetStandardValues(System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext)" /> is an exhaustive list of possible values; <see langword="false" /> if other values are possible.
trans-unit.target: 如果從 <see langword="true" /> 傳回的 <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter.StandardValuesCollection" /> 是可能值的獨占清單則為 <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TargetConverter.GetStandardValues(System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext)" />，如果其他的值為可能則為 <see langword="false" />。
這是僅供內部使用的類別。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext" /> that provides a format context.
Returns a value that indicates whether this object supports a standard set of values that can be picked from a list, using the specified context.
trans-unit.target: 使用指定內容傳回值，表示這個物件是否支援可以從清單選取的標準值集合。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TargetConverter.GetStandardValues(System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext)" /> should be called to find a common set of values the object supports; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果應該呼叫 <see cref="M:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TargetConverter.GetStandardValues(System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext)" /> 以尋找物件支援的通用值集合，則為 <see langword="true" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。
這是僅供內部使用的類別。
